  "text": [
    "Card in pew pocket",
    "announces,",
    "\u201cI am here.\u201d",
    "I made only one statement",
    "because of a bad winter.",
    "Grease is the word; grease",
    "is the way",
    "I am feeling.",
    "Real life emergencies or",
    "flubbing behind the scenes.",
    "As a child,",
    "I was abandoned",
    "in a story",
    "made of trees.",
    "Here\u2019s the small",
    "gasp",
    "of this clearing",
    "come \u201cupon\u201d \u201cagain\u201d"
  ],
  "title": "The Way",
  "year": ""
}